  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; required levels are met or exceeded at MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification has been performed and all credibility gaps have been closed. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; structured Context of Use is conveyed through the bound requirement and claim prose rather than a discrete hasContextOfUse node.",
