    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors assessed at MRL 5. Required levels met or exceeded for every factor. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th percentile NIH index below FDA threshold. Independent analyst verification completed. Systematic bias characterized and bounded within UQ budget. Assessment team concludes the CFD hemolysis model has sufficient credibility for the intended VAD decision context as described in the bound requirement and claim.",
